{"tid":1978275,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特區政府表示中聯辦是根據《基本法》第22條設立的機構之一","createTime":"2020-04-18T14:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T17:04:23.000Z","uid":326897,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8c45e8d7ddc7f61a00f2bd83ff4df90427acc251","tid":1978275,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"政府指中聯辦是中央按基本法設立機構 須遵守香港法律<br />\n2020-04-18 HKT 22:35<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521412-20200418.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521412-20200418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDu6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=0bb6db06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521412-20200418.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=abe98170\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521412-20200418.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府指中聯辦是中央按基本法設立機構 須遵守香港法律<br />\n中聯辦星期五發表聲明，指港澳辦和中聯辦是中央授權專責處理香港事務的機構，不是《基本法》第22條所指的一般意義上的中央人民政府所屬各部門，有權代表中央政府行使監督權。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府傍晚回應傳媒查詢，發言人表示，中聯辦是中央政府在香港，根據《基本法》第22條設立的機構之一， 須按《基本法》遵守香港的法律。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有黃底手足做發言人篤支那辦背脊喎</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d4e91742255612cc68d3d9ef28237d00041750","tid":1978275,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7429b8e0b5238f88117ace45de333827ccb7865a","tid":1978275,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:51:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國查黑警違反人權 最後2日deadline</span></span></strong><br />\n<a hre